(2968, 146, 'rows_0_col3_b', '<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-127 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/long-term-partnerships.jpg\" alt=\"long-term-partnerships\" width=\"750\" height=\"492\" />\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\">Long term partnerships</h3>\r\nWe’re never in it for the short term. Our goal is to plan and execute a sales strategy that will lead to long term, sustainable and profitable growth.\r\n\r\nWe work with our clients to constantly review, evaluate and build on successes so you can continue to innovate, launch new products and conquer new markets.'),
